Class XPathResult

      • getSnapshotNodes

        public java.util.List<DOMNode> getSnapshotNodes()
        Returns the list of nodes when the result type is XPathResultType.ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE or XPathResultType.UNORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE. This list do not change with document mutations, but some elements may no longer exist in the current document as a result of these mutations.
        当结果类型为XPathResultType.ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE或XPathResultType.UNORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE时，返回节点列表。该列表不会随文档突变而变化，但是由于这些突变，某些元素可能不再存在于当前文档中。
        Returns:
        the list of nodes when the result type is XPathResultType.ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE or XPathResultType.UNORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE. 结果类型为或时的节点列表。
